Wow.

12:15.791 --> 12:16.791
What is this?

12:16.958 --> 12:18.916
Rain. Rain!

12:19.083 --> 12:21.207
Oh, finally we have rain!

12:24.541 --> 12:27.790
Dad, race you to the light!

12:27.791 --> 12:29.041
