Fastest cub in the world.

13:09.166 --> 13:10.416
Thank you.

13:11.916 --> 13:13.166
Mufasa...

13:13.291 --> 13:14.290
that's enough.

13:14.291 --> 13:17.000
Mufasa, come back now.

13:24.083 --> 13:26.250
Mufasa, stay there!
I'm coming, son.

13:40.666 --> 13:42.458
-  Father!
- Mufasa!

13:49.250 --> 13:50.250
Mufasa?

13:51.208 --> 13:52.875
I'll catch you on the turn.

13:53.041 --> 13:54.458
Find my voice.

13:54.708 --> 13:56.250
Find my voice!

13:56.416 --> 13:57.583
Mom!

14:06.875 --> 14:10.208
Mufasa, the cliff is too high,
but you can cross at the dam.

14:10.375 --> 14:12.583
Come on, Mufasa,
you can do this.

14:12.750 --> 14:14.291
Find your mother's voice.

14:14.458 --> 14:16.291
Listen
to your father, Mufasa!

14:16.458 --> 14:17.791
Listen to us!

14:20.833 --> 14:21.875
Afia, he's there.

14:22.541 --> 14:24.166
-  Mom!
-  He's there!

14:24.625 --> 14:26.125
-  Mother!
- Mufasa!

14:28.750 --> 14:30.958
Find your footing
one step at a time.

14:31.125 --> 14:32.457
-  I can't.
- You can do this.

14:32.458 --> 14:33.708
I'm right here.

14:47.583 --> 14:49.166
Mufasa!

15:41.916 --> 15:43.791
Mom?

15:44.416 --> 15:45.416
Dad?

15:46.500 --> 15:47.583
Can you hear me?

15:49.250 --> 15:50.375
Is anyone out there?

15:54.000 --> 15:55.000
Mom?

15:57.000 --> 15:58.083
Please.

15:59.583 --> 16:00.750
I'm scared.

16:02.500 --> 16:03.625
I'm scared.

16:07.666 --> 16:10.541
<i>The floodwaters
joined a distant river,</i>

16:10.708 --> 16:14.458
<i>carried Mufasa far
from his mother and father.</i>

16:14.625 --> 16:16.750
<i>Beyond all that he knew.</i>

16:44.291 --> 16:46.207
Hello.

16:46.208 --> 16:49.166
I'm Taka, son of Obasi.
What's your name?

16:49.333 --> 16:50.458
Mufasa.

16:50.625 --> 16:52.333
I'm not allowed
to talk to Outsiders,

16:52.500 --> 16:54.208
but I have a secret...

16:54.375 --> 16:56.375
...and I really
want to tell you.

16:56.541 --> 16:58.375
- What's the secret?
-  I'll get in trouble.

16:58.541 --> 16:59.541
Please, just tell me.

16:59.666 --> 17:01.333
Uh... I don't know.

17:01.500 --> 17:02.541
Just tell me!

17:02.708 --> 17:04.874
Okay.
You're about to be eaten.

17:07.625 --> 17:09.250
I hate secrets!

17:11.000 --> 17:12.540
- Swim!
- But I can't!

17:12.708 --> 17:14.333
- You have to swim.
- I don't know how!

17:14.583 --> 17:17.583
All right. Chin up, then walk
underwater really fast.

17:17.750 --> 17:18.958
I can't!

17:19.125 --> 17:21.583
Come on, Mufasa. Faster!

17:23.290 --> 17:25.290
Help me, Taka! Help me!

17:39.000 --> 17:40.375
I told you to wait for me.

17:40.541 --> 17:41.833
It's not my fault, Mum.

17:42.000 --> 17:44.500
I came down for a drink
and saw him floating by.

17:44.666 --> 17:46.625
I'd like you to meet Mufasa.

17:46.791 --> 17:48.499
You're lucky
those crocs were young

17:48.500 --> 17:50.291
and afraid to fight. Let's go!

17:50.458 --> 17:51.958
We can't just leave him here.

17:52.208 --> 17:53.875
Rules are rules, Taka.

17:54.041 --> 17:56.375
Obasi will never accept
a stray.

17:56.541 --> 18:00.291
I'm not a stray.
I'm just... lost.

18:00.458 --> 18:01.458
See?

18:02.375 --> 18:03.875
He's just lost.

18:04.916 --> 18:06.291
There was a...
a flood.

18:07.208 --> 18:09.083
My parents,
they tried to save me.

18:12.041 --> 18:13.666
Do you know which way is home?

18:15.458 --> 18:16.541
Home?

18:16.791 --> 18:19.666
To be lost
is to learn the way.

18:20.583 --> 18:21.750
Call me Eshe.

18:21.916 --> 18:23.000
I'm tired, Eshe.

18:23.583 --> 18:25.124
Come on, it's this way.

18:42.750 --> 18:43.958
Come on, Mufasa.

18:52.916 --> 18:54.958
Is this <i>Milele?</i>

18:55.833 --> 18:57.166
No, my love.

19:03.083 --> 19:05.083
I was trying to nap, Eshe.

19:05.250 --> 19:07.583
The all-important nap
of kings,

19:07.750 --> 19:10.375
only to be awoken
by the disgusting,

19:10.541 --> 19:13.125
hideous, revolting stench
of a stray.

19:13.291 --> 19:14.416
When we come upon an Outsider,

19:14.583 --> 19:16.958
tell me, what do we do?

19:17.125 --> 19:18.875
Obasi, I know.

19:19.041 --> 19:20.041
Eat it.

19:20.208 --> 19:22.958
But I found him, Dad.
I saved his life.

19:23.125 --> 19:26.666
Taka, we do not associate
with Outsiders.

19:26.833 --> 19:29.666
The only true bond is blood.

19:29.833 --> 19:32.750
I've heard stories of lions
twice our size.

